In the INTEREST OF B.H.A., Minor Child, J.R., Mother, Petitioner-Appellant, M.A., Father, Respondent-Appellee. No. 18-0813 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 5, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A mother appeals the district court's denial of her petition to terminate the incarcerated father's parental rights. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
